---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - The Realm of Patterns" description="Learn about The Realm of Patterns — a personal energy reading platform based on real planetary data.">
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="page-container">
      <header class="page-header">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
      </header>

      <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-symbol">◎</div>
        <blockquote class="hero-quote">
          "Your energy pattern isn't your destiny — it's your starting point. The journey is yours."
        </blockquote>
      </section>

      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>What We Do</h2>
        <p>
          The Realm of Patterns maps your unique energy profile across 8 core dimensions based on
          real planetary data. Unlike traditional astrology that gives you a static reading, we track
          how your pattern interacts with today's cosmic conditions in real-time.
        </p>
        <p>
          Your daily check-in measures your energy across 8 dimensions, while today's planetary
          positions show how the current sky is activating your birth pattern. The result is
          a living picture of your energy — not who you are forever, but how you're showing up right now.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>The 8 Dimensions</h2>
        <div class="dimensions-list">
          <div class="dimension-item">
            <span class="dim-symbol">☉</span>
            <div class="dim-content">
              <strong>Identity</strong>
              <span>Self-expression, confidence. Who am I becoming?</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="dimension-item">
            <span class="dim-symbol">♄</span>
            <div class="dim-content">
              <strong>Structure</strong>
              <span>Stability, discipline. What grounds me?</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="dimension-item">
            <span class="dim-symbol">☿</span>
            <div class="dim-content">
              <strong>Mind</strong>
              <span>Communication, learning. How do I understand?</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="dimension-item">
            <span class="dim-symbol">♀</span>
            <div class="dim-content">
              <strong>Heart</strong>
              <span>Love, beauty, harmony. What do I treasure?</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="dimension-item">
            <span class="dim-symbol">♃</span>
            <div class="dim-content">
              <strong>Growth</strong>
              <span>Exploration, meaning. Where am I expanding?</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="dimension-item">
            <span class="dim-symbol">♂</span>
            <div class="dim-content">
              <strong>Drive</strong>
              <span>Energy, action, courage. What moves me?</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="dimension-item">
            <span class="dim-symbol">☽</span>
            <div class="dim-content">
              <strong>Connection</strong>
              <span>Relationships, empathy. Who do I love?</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="dimension-item">
            <span class="dim-symbol">♆</span>
            <div class="dim-content">
              <strong>Awareness</strong>
              <span>Intuition, presence. What witnesses?</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="content-section">
        <h2>Our Belief</h2>
        <p>
          We believe your energy pattern is a starting point, not a prison. Awareness creates choice.
          By understanding your patterns — both light and shadow — you gain the power to work with
          them rather than be unconsciously driven by them.
        </p>
        <p>
          The algorithm is open. The transformation is yours.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="cta-section">
        <h3>Ready to See Your Pattern?</h3>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/discover" class="cta-primary">Try It Free</a>
          <a href="/reading" class="cta-secondary">Today's Reading</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    --gold: #d4a854;
    --dark: #0a0908;
    --dark-surface: #141210;
    --text: #f0e8d8;
    --text-muted: rgba(240, 232, 216, 0.6);

    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    background: var(--dark);
    color: var(--text);
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;
  }

  .page-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .hero-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 168, 84, 0.2);
  }

  .hero-symbol {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-quote {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content-section strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .dimensions-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .dimensions-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .dimension-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: var(--dark-surface);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 168, 84, 0.1);
  }

  .dim-symbol {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(212, 168, 84, 0.1);
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .dim-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .dim-content strong {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .dim-content span {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    background: var(--dark-surface);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 168, 84, 0.2);
  }

  .cta-section h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-primary {
    padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--dark);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .cta-primary:hover {
    background: #e5b964;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(212, 168, 84, 0.3);
  }

  .cta-secondary {
    padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .cta-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(212, 168, 84, 0.1);
  }
</style>
